able impacts.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">That shift is the foundation of both Not Bo=
ring the newsletter and Not Boring Capital. I&#8217;m obviously biased rega=
rding the importance of storytelling, but I&#8217;ve spent every day for th=
