 line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">Ratio of positive to negative stories</p></=
li><li style=3D"margin-bottom: 3.75px; margin-left: 7.5px; margin-right: 0;=
 margin-top: 3.75px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1=
a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">Consistency of positive =
or negative attributes&nbsp;</p></li><li style=3D"margin-bottom: 3.75px; ma=
